parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can lead to increased stopping distances, accidents, and injuries, as the vehicle may not respond as expected to braking input.
symptoms: The vehicle does not slow down or stop when the brake pedal is depressed
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the vehicle takes longer than expected to come to a stop
the vehicle does not respond immediately to braking input.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Body Control Module (BCM) Failure due to Water Ingress
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the BCM can cause various electrical systems in the vehicle to malfunction, leading to safety issues, inconvenience, and costly repairs.
symptoms: Multiple electrical systems malfunction
such as lights
wipers
and mirrors
the vehicle's computer systems may shut down
the vehicle may experience intermittent electrical issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sunroof drainage system can cause water to accumulate and leak into the vehicle's electrical components, leading to corrosion, malfunction, and failure of critical systems.
symptoms: Water leaks into the vehicle
water accumulates in the sunroof drainage system
electrical systems malfunction
musty odor or water spots in the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Faulty Passenger Front Seat Bottom Assembly Causing Airbag Light and SRS System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Passenger Front Seat Bottom Assembly can cause the airbag light to illuminate, indicating a critical safety issue, and potentially leading to airbag deployment failures in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light on the dashboard illuminates
indicating a problem with the Supplemental Restraint System (SRS)
and the vehicle's diagnostic system generates a code (B00AO-02) indicating a fault with the Passenger Front Seat Bottom Assembly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the moon roof glass can cause a distraction to the driver, potentially leading to an accident, and may also cause physical harm to occupants from falling glass shards.
symptoms: The moon roof glass shatters without any impact or warning
glass shards fall into the vehicle
no warning lights are illuminated.
